# Scanned PDF Content

## Page 1

Franco Belli Plumbing & Heating & Sons, Inc.

Plumbers LIC. # 2083 Fire Supp. LIC. #774A
165 Second Avenue, Brooklyn New York 11215-4616
(718) 965-4976 * 965-4977 Fax (718) 965-2737

6/12/2025
TO: ESTIMATING

Regarding: SCA PS162Q - PLAYGROUND REDEVELOPMENT / PATH OF TRAVEL PLAYGROUND
REDEVELOPMENT / FLOOD ELIMINATION — 201-02 53" Ave, Queens NY 11364

We propose the following work as per drawings P001, PO61, P101 dated 1/31/25. Plumbing Specifications
Section 15

Project Number — 25-026443
We will install all new piping and equipment as per NYC plumbing code. We propose the following scope:

1) Provide necessary cutting and capping of existing plumbing pipes at active source as per Drawings.

2) Furnish and install new (6) drinking fountains, (3) water closets, (2) lavatories, (2) floor drains, (1) urinal as per
Drawings

3) Make new connections to existing water, sanitary, and vent lines as per Drawings.

4) Includes DOB inspections and sign-off.

Total PLA Price = $151,000
(One Hundred Fifty-One Thousand)

Notes/Exclusions:

1) Plumbers will cut and cap all plumbing at active source. Removal of existing pipe and fixtures by others.

2) No demolition or openings in walls, floors, or ceilings. No backflow cross connection PE/RA drawings.

3) We will attend all CID plumbing inspections, however no flow/flood tests or camera inspections.

4) No additional work, other then what is stated above, shall be part of this proposal. No site, main, or sewer work.
5) No excavation, cement work, back-filling, bedding and/or restoration. No concrete scanning or x-rays.

6) No patching, painting, chopping, fire-stopping, lead or copper flashings. No coring. No disinfection. No manlift.
7) No electrical work of any kind. No temporary work of any kind. No asbestos removal. No camera TV inspections.
8) No HVAC work including fire suppression, sprinklers. No work included other than plumbing work. No scaffolding
9) No access doors and/or protection. No pipe insulation. No toilet accessories. No trenching. No rubbish removal.
10) No custodial permits or security guard charges. No snaking or jet cleaning. No heat tracing. No control panels.
11) No shop drawings or as-built drawings. No provision or allowances. No bonds. No overtime.

Paul Belli Authorized Representative
President Date:
